reviewText: Classic movie. Reminded me of my childhood, dvd copy looks great and plays great.

Mumfee is my all time favorite animated movie! It brings back such memories whenever I watch it!

This movie is pure magic! You will be happy you bought this! I can't wait for it to be on DVD!

I love mumfie best movie ever!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! My kids love it. I use to own it when I was very young:)
Now I have it instant streaming :)

I received the New Mumfie DVD "Mumfie's Quest" (known as Mumfie The Movie. The Movie was remastered & Restored and excellent picture quality. The Enjoy the DVD alot. The DVD also feature two Bouns Features: "Omitted Scene & Song" & "Early Mumfie storyboard Animation." I give this DVD a 11/10. Britt Allcroft (Creator of Thomas & Friends and Shining Time Station) did a great job. Look for the New Volume in the Mumfie DVD collection soon. :)
